# Formaroute - Auto-École Domont
# Règles et Conventions du Projet

## 🎯 Vision du Projet

Site vitrine world-class pour l'auto-école Formaroute à Domont (95330).
Design premium bleu/rouge, animations fluides, SEO local agressif.

---

## 📁 Structure du Projet

```
src/
├── app/                    # Next.js App Router (pages et API)
├── components/
│   ├── ui/                 # Composants shadcn/ui
│   ├── layout/             # Header, Footer, Navigation
│   ├── sections/           # Sections réutilisables (Hero, Services, etc.)
│   └── common/             # Composants génériques (Button, Card, etc.)
├── lib/                    # Utilitaires, clients (Sanity, Resend)
├── hooks/                  # Custom React hooks
├── types/                  # Types TypeScript
└── data/                   # Données statiques (villes, formations, etc.)
```

---

## 🛠️ Stack Technologique

- **Framework**: Next.js 14+ (App Router)
- **Language**: TypeScript (strict mode)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS 3.4+
- **UI Components**: shadcn/ui
- **Animations**: Framer Motion 11+
- **Forms**: React Hook Form + Zod
- **Icons**: Lucide React
- **CMS**: Sanity v3
- **Email**: Resend
- **Booking**: Cal.com embed

---

## 🎨 Design System

### Couleurs Principales

```css
/* Bleu Formaroute - Confiance */
--formaroute-blue-50: #eff6ff;
--formaroute-blue-100: #dbeafe;
--formaroute-blue-200: #bfdbfe;
--formaroute-blue-300: #93c5fd;
--formaroute-blue-400: #60a5fa;
--formaroute-blue-500: #3b82f6;
--formaroute-blue-600: #2563eb;
--formaroute-blue-700: #1d4ed8;
--formaroute-blue-800: #1e40af;
--formaroute-blue-900: #1e3a8a;

/* Rouge Formaroute - Énergie */
--formaroute-red-50: #fef2f2;
--formaroute-red-100: #fee2e2;
--formaroute-red-200: #fecaca;
--formaroute-red-300: #fca5a5;
--formaroute-red-400: #f87171;
--formaroute-red-500: #ef4444;
